komorebi (2.1-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Modernized build system for Debian 13 (Trixie)
  * Migrated from webkit2gtk-4.0 to webkit2gtk-4.1
  * Updated install paths to FHS standards
  * Added Docker-based reproducible build environment
  * Switched to automatic dependency detection (dpkg-shlibdeps)
  * Updated CMake minimum version to 3.16

